comments:
I initially thought about taking notes but the pace of the study was too quick for that, so I just remembered as best as I could. 

I almost always broke the words into two sections e.g. wopy-cow, gafy-koe, buvi-koh, ze-teeco.

The hardest part was the wopycow and wopycopw variation, but the training made it very easy.

Very interesting study, thank you! =)
